The '''Embassy of Bahrain''' in [[Washington, D.C.]] is the [[diplomatic mission]] of the [[Bahrain| Kingdom of Bahrain]] to the [[United States]]. It is located at 3502 International Drive, [[Northwest, Washington, D.C.]], in the [[Cleveland Park]] neighborhood.<ref>http://www.embassy.org/embassies/bh.html</ref>
The embassy also operates a [[Consul (representative)|Consulate-General]] in [[New York City]].

The Ambassador is H.E. Shaikh Abdullah Bin Mohammed Bin Rashid Al Khalifa.

